| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5546 — Recovery Inhibition (underground)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1bcfa757-f97e-5bcd-a6d5-a9b882fd23af"
